  "prompt": "Where can I found a large range of formal and evening wear in Gold Coast?",
  "response": "If you're looking for formal and evening wear in the Gold Coast area, there are several places you can check out:\n\n1. **Pacific Fair Shopping Centre**: Located in Broadbeach, this is one of the largest shopping centers in Queensland. It offers a wide range of high-end and boutique stores that carry formal and evening wear, such as David Jones and Myer.\n\n2. **Harbour Town Outlet Shopping Centre**: Situated in Biggera Waters, Harbour Town offers discounted prices on designer brands. You might find great deals on formal and evening attire here.\n\n3. **Cavill Avenue, Surfers Paradise**: This area is known for its variety of shops and boutiques that offer unique and stylish options for formal wear.\n\n4. **The Strand at Coolangatta**: It is another shopping venue that could have what you're looking for, with various fashion outlets available.\n\n5. **Local Boutiques**: Explore smaller, independent boutiques throughout the Gold Coast for unique pieces. Areas like Burleigh Heads, Broadbeach, and Surfers Paradise often have boutique shops that carry a range of evening and formal wear.\n\n6. **Formalwear Hire**: For one-time events, you might consider hiring formal wear from places like Ferrari Formalwear or Black Jacket Suiting.\n\nMake sure to check online for specific store hours and availability, as these can change.",
